BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:-s3KuKg3iU-RtGTOLlJw1
SUMMARY:1st
DTSTAMP:20260401T044550Z
DTSTART:20260408T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:MAXIMIZE YOUR MEMBERSHIP Congratulations\, you have joined the 
	Chamber of Commerce! Now what? Here is where you learn to use the SUPER 6 
	Tools\, when you log in to your MIC \\(Member Information Center\\). Maxim
	ize Your Membership 101 workshop is designed to educate our valued members
	 on the benefits of using your Chamber Master access. We will also cover n
	etworking opportunities and advocacy that are available to you as a member
	 of the Renton Chamber of Commerce. This training session will equip you w
	ith the ability to navigate and utilize your MIC Tools to effectively prom
	ote your business reaching over 10k potential customers. Posting Jobs\, Ev
	ents\, Member 2 Member and Hot Deals\, and more\, will be shown. MYM101 is
	 an essential to for new members onboarding and current members who need a
	 refresher course\, who want MAXimize Your Membership!  Our membership is 
	similar to a gym... the more you use it\, the better the results!  We also
