BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:VQ6PC4Yd3Zl0fd3kDFqB-
SUMMARY:Entrepreneurial Mash Up
DTSTAMP:20260401T044550Z
DTSTART:20260408T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description    Entrepreneurial Mash Up The city's doers\, dream
	ers\, and makers in one place. Date: Tuesday\, April 7 Time: 5:30-7:30 PM 
	Location: Columbia Tower Club Price: $35 Come meet the communities shaping
	 Seattle's entrepreneurial soul. Columbia Tower Club\, GSBA\, and Entrepre
	neurs' Organization are coming together to host an evening built for conne
	ction\, curiosity\, and shared momentum. This is your chance to learn what
	 each organization brings to the region's business landscape and meet the 
	people who make those missions real. Expect conversations that open doors\
	, introductions that expand your world\, and a room filled with good energ
	y and big ideas. Show up ready to connect. Leave with a wider circle and a
	 stronger network. This event is for active GSBA members only - you must b
	e logged in to your InfoHub to purchase tickets. Due to extremely limited 
	capacity\, each organization has access to 35 tickets. About the Hosts  Ab
	out GSBA GSBA is Washington State's LGBTQ\\+ and allied chamber of commerc
	e. GSBA invests in economic vitality\, business development\, and inclusiv
	e leadership through programming\, advocacy\, and the GSBA Scholarship & E
	ducation Fund. About EO Seattle EO Seattle is the local chapter of the Ent
	repreneurs' Organization\, a global network of founders and business owner
	s committed to learning\, growth\, and community. Members connect through 
	peer learning\, events\, and leadership development opportunities. About C
	olumbia Tower Club Located at the top of Columbia Center\, Columbia Tower 
	Club is Seattle's premier private business and social club. The Club conve
	nes leaders from across industries for dining\, professional connection\, 
	and memorable experiences.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detail
	s/entrepreneurial-mash-up/18425344/2026-04-07T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Ev
	ents
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/entrepreneurial-mash-up/1
	8425344/2026-04-07T00
LOCATION:Columbia Tower Club\, 701 5th Ave\, 75th Flr\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
