BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:QsKq6-Y44tEqF5SF5T6iJ
SUMMARY:Twatties Open Mic of the Absurd!
DTSTAMP:20260401T044551Z
DTSTART:20260414T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Twatties! Seattle’s home to the zany and insane in C
	apitol Hill. We are an absurdist open mic variety show bringing old-Seattl
	e anti-normative joy. We offer performers four minutes to try anything in 
	front of a live and engaging audience. \n\nAll performance art such as sta
	ndup\, music\, poetry\, drag\, and puppets is welcomed. We showcase local 
	art installations\, a cozy atmosphere\, and great food and drink specials 
	to make Twatties the perfect weirdo third place.\n\nInterested in performi
	ng? Showcasing your work? Or just looking for a great place to see art and
	 connect with a community? Stage time sign-ups fill fast\, so arrive at 7:
	00 P.M. when the list goes live for the best chance to perform. Audience m
	embers wishing to witness the cozy chaos must note the show begins at 8:00
	 P.M. and has no intermission.”\n\nSaint John's Bar and Eatery\n\n719 E Pi
	ke St\, Seattle\, WA 98122\n\nMondays\, starting April 6th.\n\nSign-ups 7:
	00pm\n\nShow 8:00pm\n\nEVENT IS FREE\n\n21\\+ Must show valid ID\n\nhttps:
	//seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/twatties-open-mic-of-the-absurd/18
	431464/2026-04-13T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/twatties-open-mic-of-the-
	absurd/18431464/2026-04-13T00
LOCATION:Saint John's Bar and Eatery\, 719 E Pike St\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
